data.body:
- VSCode Version: 1.4.0
- OS Version: Ubuntu 14

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Open Scss/Sass file, or choose that language
2. Use `@at-root`, example:

```
.head {
  height: 64px;
  line-height: 64px;
  background-color: #f2f2f2;
  margin-top: $gradientHeight;

  @at-root #{&}__title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #339;
    margin-left: 2rem;
    display: inline-block;
  }
```

[Screenshot example](http://i.imgur.com/wboc6Mp.png)

It has been reported earlier too - #4524
